{"blogid": "124355880", "writerAge": "码龄2年", "writerBlogNum": "22", "writerCollect": "2127", "writerComment": "713", "writerFan": "1949", "writerGrade": "5级", "writerIntegral": "2872", "writerName": "耀 星", "writerProfileAdress": "writer_image\\profile_124355880.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "19562", "writerRankWeekly": "114921", "writerThumb": "1196", "writerVisitNum": "70410", "blog_read_count": "41267", "blog_time": "于 2022-04-24 11:07:40 发布", "blog_title": "IDEA各种玩法（开发者必备）", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"htmledit_views\" id=\"content_views\">\n<p id=\"main-toc\"><strong>目录</strong></p>\n<p id=\"%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7%E9%94%AE%EF%BC%88%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E7%A0%81%E5%AD%97%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%89-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7%E9%94%AE%EF%BC%88%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E7%A0%81%E5%AD%97%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%89\">        </a><a href=\"#%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7%E9%94%AE%EF%BC%88%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E7%A0%81%E5%AD%97%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%89\">🌾快捷键（提高码字速度）</a></p>\n<p id=\"%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7%E9%94%AE-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7%E9%94%AE\">        </a><a href=\"#%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7%E9%94%AE\">🤡自定义快捷键</a></p>\n<p id=\"%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%8A%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%8A%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\">        </a><a href=\"#%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%8A%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\">🐢搜索插件方法及安装</a></p>\n<p id=\"%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7%E9%94%AE%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%EF%BC%88%E8%AE%A9%E4%BD%A0%E8%84%B1%E7%A6%BB%E9%BC%A0%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%89-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7%E9%94%AE%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%EF%BC%88%E8%AE%A9%E4%BD%A0%E8%84%B1%E7%A6%BB%E9%BC%A0%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%89\">        </a><a href=\"#%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7%E9%94%AE%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%EF%BC%88%E8%AE%A9%E4%BD%A0%E8%84%B1%E7%A6%BB%E9%BC%A0%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%89\">✨快捷键提示（让你脱离鼠标）</a></p>\n<p id=\"%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF\">        </a><a href=\"#%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF\">🍎设置背景</a></p>\n<p id=\"%E7%BF%BB%E8%AF%91-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#%E7%BF%BB%E8%AF%91\">        </a><a href=\"#%E7%BF%BB%E8%AF%91\">📈翻译</a></p>\n<p id=\"%E7%AE%80%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#%E7%AE%80%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6\">        </a><a href=\"#%E7%AE%80%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6\">🍓简体中文</a></p>\n<p id=\"%E5%BD%A9%E8%99%B9%E6%8B%AC%E5%8F%B7-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#%E5%BD%A9%E8%99%B9%E6%8B%AC%E5%8F%B7\">        </a><a href=\"#%E5%BD%A9%E8%99%B9%E6%8B%AC%E5%8F%B7\">🌈七彩括号</a></p>\n<p id=\"%E5%B0%8F%E5%9C%B0%E5%9B%BE-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#%E5%B0%8F%E5%9C%B0%E5%9B%BE\">        </a><a href=\"#%E5%B0%8F%E5%9C%B0%E5%9B%BE\">🤙小地图</a></p>\n<p id=\"%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1\">        </a><a href=\"#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1\">🎯代码统计</a></p>\n<p id=\"%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E6%97%B6%E5%BA%8F%E5%9B%BE-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E6%97%B6%E5%BA%8F%E5%9B%BE\">        </a><a href=\"#%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E6%97%B6%E5%BA%8F%E5%9B%BE\">💎生成方法时序图</a></p>\n<p id=\"%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%A1%A5%E5%85%A8-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%A1%A5%E5%85%A8\">        </a><a href=\"#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%A1%A5%E5%85%A8\">🥝代码补全</a></p>\n<p id=\"%C2%A0%E9%98%B2%E6%B2%89%E8%BF%B7-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#%C2%A0%E9%98%B2%E6%B2%89%E8%BF%B7\">        </a><a href=\"#%C2%A0%E9%98%B2%E6%B2%89%E8%BF%B7\">🖐防沉迷</a></p>\n<p id=\"LeetCode%E5%88%B7%E9%A2%98-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#LeetCode%E5%88%B7%E9%A2%98\">        </a><a href=\"#LeetCode%E5%88%B7%E9%A2%98\">🏓LeetCode刷题</a></p>\n<p id=\"%C2%A0%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E6%B3%A8%E9%87%8A%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#%C2%A0%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E6%B3%A8%E9%87%8A%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6\">        </a><a href=\"#%C2%A0%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E6%B3%A8%E9%87%8A%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6\">🎽快速生成文档注释</a></p>\n<p id=\"%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\">        </a><a href=\"#%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\">🐳扫描代码问题</a></p>\n<p id=\"%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%B7%B4%E5%B7%B4%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83%E6%A3%80%E6%9F%A5%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%C2%A0-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%B7%B4%E5%B7%B4%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83%E6%A3%80%E6%9F%A5%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%C2%A0\">        </a><a href=\"#%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%B7%B4%E5%B7%B4%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83%E6%A3%80%E6%9F%A5%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%C2%A0\">🧣阿里巴巴编码规范检查工具 </a></p>\n<p id=\"%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E7%9D%80%E8%89%B2-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E7%9D%80%E8%89%B2\">        </a><a href=\"#%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E7%9D%80%E8%89%B2\">🍋日志信息着色</a></p>\n<hr id=\"hr-toc\"/>\n<p></p>\n<p>大家好，我是耀星🌟，本篇将详细介绍IDEA快捷键及插件，让你学习和开发事半功倍。IDEA的牛逼，众所皆知，不论是用来学习还是开发都是首选的IDE，拉爆其他开发工具，让你爱上代码。很多隐藏的功能等待着你去发现🔍。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"555\" src=\"image\\e2280ec0e5904537909571e9c022c863.png\" width=\"924\"/></p>\n<h1 id=\"%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7%E9%94%AE%EF%BC%88%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E7%A0%81%E5%AD%97%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%89\">🌾快捷键（提高码字速度）</h1>\n<p>1.快速生成main方法:psvm +Tab或 main+Tab</p>\n<p>2.快速生成System.out.prinltn():sout+Tab</p>\n<p>3.删除一行:Ctrl+Y</p>\n<p>4.切换java文件（前提是工程有多个.java文件）</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"45\" src=\"image\\77ccd24e7cc04eccaebb76a50e643fc0.png\" width=\"1084\"/></p>\n<p>Alt+右箭头 或 Alt+左箭头</p>\n<p>5,复制选中行到下一行:Ctrl+D</p>\n<p>6.撤销上一步操作:Ctrl+Z</p>\n<p>7.取消撤销:Ctrl+Shift+Z</p>\n<p>8.将选中的行合并成一行:Ctrl+shift+J</p>\n<p>9.Ctrl+N:查找类文件</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"75\" src=\"image\\ed46440cea2a41e6ad4c661125ca27d4.png\" width=\"841\"/></p>\n<p>10.显示文件结构:Ctrl+F12</p>\n<p>11.显示当前文件夹路径:Ctrl+Alt+F12</p>\n<p>12.显示当前类的继承层次:Ctrl+H</p>\n<p>13.定位至下一个错误:F2</p>\n<p>14.定位到前一个错误:Shift+F2</p>\n<p>15.展开代码:Ctrl+=</p>\n<p>16.折叠代码:Ctrl+-</p>\n<p>17.选中所有：Ctrl+A</p>\n<p>18.复制:Ctrl+C</p>\n<p>19.剪切:Ctrl+X:</p>\n<p>20.粘贴:Ctrl+V</p>\n<p>21.定位到文件的某一行:Ctrl+G</p>\n<p>22.选中的行多行注释:Ctrl+Shift+/</p>\n<p>23.选中的行注释或取消注释:Ctrl+/</p>\n<p>24.运行当前文件:Ctrl+Shift+F10</p>\n<p>25.提示方法的参数:Ctrl+P</p>\n<p>26.跳到文件尾:Ctrl+End</p>\n<p>27.跳到文件头:Ctrl+Home</p>\n<p>28.选中的行代码格式化:Ctrl+Alt+L</p>\n<p>29.在当前文件进行文本查找:Ctrl+R</p>\n<p>30.选中的行打断点或取消断点:Ctrl+F8</p>\n<h1 id=\"%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7%E9%94%AE\">🤡自定义快捷键</h1>\n<p>File-&gt;Setting-&gt;KeyMap</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"885\" src=\"image\\288d4ae203b64bebae8cb7259a74ddb9.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"897\" src=\"image\\4e76124ac8a947938aec63991af43d9f.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<h1 id=\"%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%8A%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\">🐢搜索插件方法及安装</h1>\n<p>File-&gt;Settings-&gt;Plugins</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"876\" src=\"image\\15a6e87c42914e3ea6ce38c8bde5124d.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<h1 id=\"%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7%E9%94%AE%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%EF%BC%88%E8%AE%A9%E4%BD%A0%E8%84%B1%E7%A6%BB%E9%BC%A0%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%89\">✨快捷键提示（让你脱离鼠标）</h1>\n<p>安装插件：Key Promoter X</p>\n<p>右侧列表展开，会展示你近期使用的功能进行，需要经常使用的我们就可以记住快捷键，提高效率。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"290\" src=\"image\\e5d6c2bdd17149359d8d4e4597c9673f.png\" width=\"662\"/></p>\n<h1 id=\"%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF\">🍎设置背景</h1>\n<p>安装插件：Backgroud Image Plus +</p>\n<p>设置壁纸：File-&gt;Settings-&gt;Appearance-&gt;BackgoundImage</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"883\" src=\"image\\b84701e9f7d14b57b4cf8c3b5a8c73cd.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<p>有对象的放自己对象，没对象的自己new一个呗。 </p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"1009\" src=\"image\\16042fb60c804cab98965fabacd9eaad.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<p> 设置随机切换壁纸</p>\n<p>Settings-&gt;Background Image Plus</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"886\" src=\"image\\a01d65a4694c43eb8786072ac8073610.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<h1 id=\"%E7%BF%BB%E8%AF%91\">📈翻译</h1>\n<p>安装插件：Translation</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"343\" src=\"image\\ef627c38fc584b169643d776048a79d5.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"829\" src=\"image\\401d2106dc6b48429f7607dbf92a9869.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<p>是不是非常的方便！！！ </p>\n<h1 id=\"%E7%AE%80%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6\">🍓简体中文</h1>\n<p>安装插件：Chinese (Simplified)</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"516\" src=\"image\\f6770fee1e9d412bbdcbcb468a0ae804.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<h1 id=\"%E5%BD%A9%E8%99%B9%E6%8B%AC%E5%8F%B7\">🌈七彩括号</h1>\n<p>安装插件：Rainbow Brackets</p>\n<p>面对这样的一个表达式：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-java\">boolean flag = (true?false:(false?true:(false == true?false:true)))</code></pre>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"91\" src=\"image\\612eaafcfc98414782db6dfade16dd21.png\" width=\"1152\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"469\" src=\"image\\db0ac18407c44f8ebbf6690b93a79bb6.png\" width=\"825\"/></p>\n<p>轻轻松松阅读！！！ </p>\n<p class=\"img-center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"299\" src=\"image\\401b76defb1647379b7ab06bed4c3958.png\" width=\"490\"/></p>\n<h1 id=\"%E5%B0%8F%E5%9C%B0%E5%9B%BE\">🤙小地图</h1>\n<p>安装插件：Code Glance</p>\n<p>阅读很长的代码，滚轮都滚冒烟了。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"572\" src=\"image\\ccb24b70e6a04a529269560a4e559c0f.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<h1 id=\"%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1\">🎯代码统计</h1>\n<p>安装插件：Statistic</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"888\" src=\"image\\2f1b126f8c5247bab6bab46c3eb464f3.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"261\" src=\"image\\c31649fa2a6c45a48d288312afb095a7.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<h1 id=\"%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E6%97%B6%E5%BA%8F%E5%9B%BE\">💎生成方法时序图</h1>\n<p>安装插件：SequenceDiagram</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"1019\" src=\"image\\6ac4b03d84bc4407b210d0d6394b309c.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<h1 id=\"%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%A1%A5%E5%85%A8\">🥝代码补全</h1>\n<p>安装插件：Codota AI</p>\n<p>IDEA自带的补全代码已经很强大，AI补全代码更加强大，越用越好用。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"445\" src=\"image\\c163d73b006a479aa5a4420d5ecac98c.png\" width=\"1044\"/></p>\n<h1 id=\"%C2%A0%E9%98%B2%E6%B2%89%E8%BF%B7\">🖐防沉迷</h1>\n<p>安装插件：StopCoding</p>\n<p>如果你经常沉迷于写代码，那么试试这个插件，设置工作时间和休息时间，别忘了起来喝杯水，走动几步，爱护身体，从你我做起💖。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"578\" src=\"image\\033ecdc326d24f5c8668b6d5cfd69a12.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<p>大家可以试试看，有惊喜🎉。 </p>\n<h1 id=\"LeetCode%E5%88%B7%E9%A2%98\">🏓LeetCode刷题</h1>\n<p>安装插件：LeetCode Editor</p>\n<p>按提示登录即可。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"959\" src=\"image\\fc154247b619409aa3189f9c949b4b13.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<h1 id=\"%C2%A0%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E6%B3%A8%E9%87%8A%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6\">🎽快速生成文档注释</h1>\n<p>安装插件：JavaDoc</p>\n<p>Windows上可以通过Alt+Insert，Mac可通过Ctrl+Enter。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"315\" src=\"image\\c5e97b598ae545ccb3def2828bb09384.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<h1 id=\"%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\">🐳扫描代码问题</h1>\n<p>安装插件：SonarLint</p>\n<p>帮助你检查代码的问题，例如性能，安全、重复等问题。新手必备。 </p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"586\" src=\"image\\486e0ce6f1cb4c4fac2d7be3634ee1da.png\" width=\"1130\"/></p>\n<h1 id=\"%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%B7%B4%E5%B7%B4%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83%E6%A3%80%E6%9F%A5%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%C2%A0\">🧣阿里巴巴编码规范检查工具 </h1>\n<p>安装插件 ：Alibaba Java Coding Guidelines</p>\n<p>提高代码质量，必不可少。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"680\" src=\"image\\69b1301e8a5b456395e5bfa62227cbd5.png\" width=\"918\"/></p>\n<h1 id=\"%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E7%9D%80%E8%89%B2\">🍋日志信息着色</h1>\n<p>安装插件：Grep Console</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"807\" src=\"image\\8f93bd0782bf45d6b40e63505e254503.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"466\" src=\"image\\de6e2ad3d8c541e78d892b10d2d0893e.png\" width=\"781\"/></p>\n<p>提示：IDEA安装的插件不是越多越好，会影响IDEA的使用性能，部分插件安装后需要重启方可使用。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">欢迎大家的点赞👍，评论📰，收藏📚。</p>\n</div>\n</div>"}